# ansible-commands 
- use the commands
  - Prints the current working directory on each host 
    ```
    ansible dev -a "pwd"
    ``` 
  - Lists the files in the current directory on each host
    ```
    ansible dev -a "ls"
    ```
  - Lists all files (including hidden ones) in the current directory on each host
    ```
    ansible dev -a "ls -a"
